Description: Async boto3 wrapper (Avalan PPA pin)
 aioboto3 provides the asyncio interface that Avalan's `vendors`
 extra uses to drive AWS services without blocking the event loop.
 It re-exports boto3's high-level resources and clients on top of
 aiobotocore. Avalan ships it in its `vendors` extras at
 `>= 15.0.0, < 16.0.0`; nothing in Debian carries it, so the
 rebuild pins 15.5.0.
